{"info": {"author": "Lucas Taniguti", "author_email": "ltaniguti@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": [], "description": "# Google IAP authentication ![Upload Python Package](https://github.com/lmtani/iap-auth/workflows/Upload%20Python%20Package/badge.svg?branch=master)\n\nThis module contains a helper class to make requests to an app running behind a Google Identity-Aware Proxy. The code was obtained from the Google [Programmatic authentication](https://cloud.google.com/iap/docs/authentication-howto#iap_make_request-python) document.\n\n\n### Install\n\n```bash\npip install iap-auth\n```\n\n### Usage\n\n```python\nfrom iap_auth import IapClient\n\nIAM_SCOPE = 'https://www.googleapis.com/auth/iam'\nOAUTH_TOKEN_URI = 'https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v4/token'\nCLIENT_ID = '<your-project-client-id>.apps.googleusercontent.com'\nURL = 'https://your-iap-protected-website.com.br'\nMETHOD = 'GET'\nkwargs = {}\n\ncli = IapClient(OAUTH_TOKEN_URI, IAM_SCOPE)\nresp = cli.make_iap_request(URL, CLIENT_ID, method=METHOD, **kwargs)\n\n# resp is a requests.Response object.\n```\n\n> If running outside Google Cloud Platform you need to specify env var GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS to point to your authorized service account.\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/lmtani/iap-auth", "keywords": "", "license": "unlicense", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "iap-auth", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/iap-auth/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/iap-auth/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/lmtani/iap-auth"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/iap-auth/0.1.5/", "requires_dist": ["requests-toolbelt", "google-auth-oauthlib"], "requires_python": "", "summary": "Performs authentication for Google Cloud Identity Aware Proxy from a service account", "version": "0.1.5", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Google IAP authentication <img alt=\"Upload Python Package\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/160d03b9bacacf531151ac18078716496b10edb6/68747470733a2f2f6769746875622e636f6d2f6c6d74616e692f6961702d617574682f776f726b666c6f77732f55706c6f6164253230507974686f6e2532305061636b6167652f62616467652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></h1>\n<p>This module contains a helper class to make requests to an app running behind a Google Identity-Aware Proxy. The code was obtained from the Google <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/iap/docs/authentication-howto#iap_make_request-python\" rel=\"nofollow\">Programmatic authentication</a> document.</p>\n<h3>Install</h3>\n<pre>pip install iap-auth\n</pre>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">iap_auth</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">IapClient</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">IAM_SCOPE</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'https://www.googleapis.com/auth/iam'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">OAUTH_TOKEN_URI</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v4/token'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CLIENT_ID</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'&lt;your-project-client-id&gt;.apps.googleusercontent.com'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">URL</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'https://your-iap-protected-website.com.br'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">METHOD</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'GET'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">kwargs</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">{}</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">cli</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">IapClient</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">OAUTH_TOKEN_URI</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">IAM_SCOPE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">resp</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">cli</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">make_iap_request</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">URL</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">CLIENT_ID</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">method</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">METHOD</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">**</span><span class=\"n\">kwargs</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># resp is a requests.Response object.</span>\n</pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>If running outside Google Cloud Platform you need to specify env var GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS to point to your authorized service account.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6801254, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "7d01a4ecfc4b6cbef3568743170c4fb1", "sha256": "0300c7fa9f03355d5d650b95115d08aea3bad1fa3ff029c2665dcb75ea8f0724"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "iap_auth-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "7d01a4ecfc4b6cbef3568743170c4fb1", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 2775, "upload_time": "2020-01-28T12:42:37", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-01-28T12:42:37.909127Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/7d/b2/5328de2f725639ef8c3c2be0b9cc0ada39f96a2bb91ef217b214baf1d227/iap_auth-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "49f67c7a6335d01069c07d847f9fa008", "sha256": "448ef5ad170146e69c21842e61e52c84c4f7f12eb1e2e6e431ac94610bb68167"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "iap-auth-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "49f67c7a6335d01069c07d847f9fa008", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2881, "upload_time": "2020-01-28T12:42:40", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-01-28T12:42:40.303368Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/27/5d/f89637ef85496705acae1f1bc0b08bb153e4fd6cbf061be90a1c97651783/iap-auth-0.0.1.tar.gz